cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.DC, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the optimization solver ADMM in the context of machine learning. It may also belong to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as it proposes a new algorithm for optimization. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as ADMM is often used in distributed computing. The paper also mentions computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY) as potential applications of the proposed algorithm.
